title: Looking for a support DUO, must be plat+.
body:
Hi there!

I have been away from the game for a while now, but I was challenger on NA last year. Getting back in to the game now with a new account on OCE.

I play ADC, pretty much all champions and I'm very good. Give me a reliable support that is able to play atleast 4-6 champs and we won't lose!

Feel free to PM me in game.

T3RoRe

replies.body: BOOMP, look up my stats and lets roll.
errr G1 .. can play a pretty big pool of support champs.. ign: realskes

Currently gold 5, but i'll put my stuff here anyway

Champs: Soraka, Thresh, Blitzcrank, Nami, Nunu, Alistar, Shen

Haven't done solid supporting in a while but i'd be cool to pick it up again.
